{"title":"每日一题：LC231 2的幂 & LC342 4的幂数","date":"2021-05-30T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 31, 2021","L":"05/31/2021","MM-DD":"05-31"},"link":"2021/05/31/刷题日记/每日一题：LC231 2的幂 & LC342 4的幂","tags":["LeetCode"],"categories":["LeetCode"],"updated":"2021-05-31T02:16:28.754Z","content":"<h1 id=\"每日一题：lc231-2的幂-&amp;-lc342-4的幂\">每日一题：LC231 2的幂 &amp; LC342 4的幂<a title=\"#每日一题：lc231-2的幂-&amp;-lc342-4的幂\" href=\"#每日一题：lc231-2的幂-&amp;-lc342-4的幂\"></a></h1>\n<p>Easy <a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/power-of-two/\" target=\"_blank\">231. 2 的幂</a>，<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/power-of-four/\" target=\"_blank\">342. 4的幂</a></p>\n<p>本文内容参考：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/power-of-two/solution/2de-mi-by-leetcode-solution-rny3/\" target=\"_blank\">LeetCode-Solution</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>一个数<code>n</code>为2的幂，当且仅当<code>n</code>为正整数，且<code>n</code>的二进制表示中仅包含1个1。</p>\n<p>两种常见的与<strong>二进制表示中最低位</strong>相关的位运算技巧：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>n &amp; (n-1)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>这个技巧可以直接将<code>n</code>二进制表示的最低为1移除。</strong></p>\n<p>因此当<code>n</code>为正整数且<code>n&amp;(n-1)=0</code>，则<code>n</code>为2的幂。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>n &amp; (-n)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>这个技巧可以直接获取<code>n</code>二进制表示的最低位的<code>1</code>。</strong></p>\n<p>因此当<code>n</code>为正整数且<code>n&amp;(-n)=n</code>，那么<code>n</code>就是2的幂。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"数据结构/哈希映射（HashMap）","link":"2021/05/31/数据结构/哈希映射（HashMap）"},"next":{"title":"HTML5","link":"2021/05/14/HTML&CSS/HTML5进阶"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/05/31/刷题日记/每日一题：LC231 2的幂 & LC342 4的幂/","toc":[{"id":"每日一题：lc231-2的幂-&amp;-lc342-4的幂","title":"每日一题：LC231 2的幂 &amp; LC342 4的幂","index":"1"}]}